==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fineer
<hw>Fi*neer"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To run in debt by
getting goods made up in a way unsuitable for the use of others, and
then threatening not to take them except on credit.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Goldsmith.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fineer</ent>⟦br⟧

